		    <title outputclass="H4H30x" xtrf="Grey" class="- topic/title ">
			      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">570.106-1</ph> Synopsis of lease awards.</title>
		    <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
			      <ol class="- topic/ol " id="d949e13">
				        <li otherprops="H5_abc"
                audience="GSAR"
                outputclass="Grey_H5_abc"
                xtrf="Grey"
                class="- topic/li ">
					          <p outputclass="H5_abc"
                  xtrf="Grey"
                  class="- topic/p "
                  id="d940e17">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						             Except for lease actions described in paragraph (b) of this section, contracting officers must synopsize in <xref href="http://www.FBO.gov"
                        scope="external"
                        format="html"
                        class="- topic/xref ">http://www.FBO.gov</xref> awards exceeding $25,000 total contract value that are likely to result in the award of any subcontracts. However, the dollar threshold is not a prohibition against publicizing an award of a smaller amount when publicizing would be advantageous to industry or to the Government.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li otherprops="H5_abc"
                audience="GSAR"
                outputclass="Grey_H5_abc"
                xtrf="Grey"
                class="- topic/li ">
					          <p outputclass="H5_abc"
                  xtrf="Grey"
                  class="- topic/p "
                  id="d940e30">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						             A notice is not required if—</p>
					          <ol class="- topic/ol " id="d949e36">
						            <li otherprops="H6_123"
                      audience="GSAR"
                      outputclass="Grey_H6_123"
                      xtrf="Grey"
                      class="- topic/li ">
							              <p outputclass="H6_123"
                        xtrf="Grey"
                        class="- topic/p "
                        id="d940e40">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                 The notice would disclose the occupant agency’s needs and the disclosure of such needs would compromise the national security; or</p>
						            </li>
						            <li otherprops="H6_123"
                      audience="GSAR"
                      outputclass="Grey_H6_123"
                      xtrf="Grey"
                      class="- topic/li ">
							              <p outputclass="H6_123"
                        xtrf="Grey"
                        class="- topic/p "
                        id="d940e49">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                 The lease—</p>
							              <ol class="- topic/ol " id="d949e55">
								                <li otherprops="H7_i_ii_iii"
                            audience="GSAR"
                            outputclass="Grey_H7_i_ii_iii"
                            xtrf="Grey"
                            class="- topic/li ">
									                  <p outputclass="H7_i_ii_iii"
                              xtrf="Grey"
                              class="- topic/p "
                              id="d940e59">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(i)</ph>
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
										                     Is for an amount not greater than the simplified lease acquisition threshold;</p>
								                </li>
								                <li otherprops="H7_i_ii_iii"
                            audience="GSAR"
                            outputclass="Grey_H7_i_ii_iii"
                            xtrf="Grey"
                            class="- topic/li ">
									                  <p outputclass="H7_i_ii_iii"
                              xtrf="Grey"
                              class="- topic/p "
                              id="d940e68">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(ii)</ph>
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
										                     Was made through a means where access to the notice of proposed lease action was provided through <xref href="http://www.FBO.gov"
                                    scope="external"
                                    format="html"
                                    class="- topic/xref ">http://www.FBO.gov</xref>; and</p>
								                </li>
								                <li otherprops="H7_i_ii_iii"
                            audience="GSAR"
                            outputclass="Grey_H7_i_ii_iii"
                            xtrf="Grey"
                            class="- topic/li ">
									                  <p outputclass="H7_i_ii_iii"
                              xtrf="Grey"
                              class="- topic/p "
                              id="d940e81">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(iii)</ph>
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
										                     Permitted the public to respond to the solicitation electronically.</p>
								                </li>
							              </ol>
						            </li>
						            <li otherprops="H6_abc"
                      outputclass="H6_abc"
                      xtrf="Grey"
                      class="- topic/li ">
							              <p audience="GSAR"
                        outputclass="Grey_H6_abc"
                        xtrf="Grey"
                        class="- topic/p "
                        id="d940e92">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                 Justifications for other than full and open competition must be posted in <xref href="http://www.FBO.gov"
                              scope="external"
                              format="html"
                              class="- topic/xref ">http://www.FBO.gov</xref>. Information exempt from public disclosure must be redacted.</p>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
			      </ol>
